Venice first appeared in the [[2010 United States census]] when it was formed along with [[Boothville, Louisiana|Boothville CDP]] from the deleted [[Boothville-Venice, Louisiana|Boothville-Venice CDP]].<ref name=2010CensusLA>{{cite web|title=2010 Census of Population - Population and Housing Unit Counts - Louisiana|url=https://www2.census.gov/library/publications/decennial/2010/cph-2/cph-2-20.pdf|website=[[United States Census Bureau]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20240402175429/https://www2.census.gov/library/publications/decennial/2010/cph-2/cph-2-20.pdf|archive-date=April 2, 2024}}</ref>

